<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />All the day long my dishonor is before me,</para>

<para style="q1">and the shame of my face has covered me</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />because of the voice of him who rebukes and insults,</para>

<para style="q1">because of the enemy and the avenger.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />All this has come on us; yet we have not forgotten you</para>

<para style="q1">or dealt falsely with your covenant.</para>
